data.title: Convert India Time to Central Time
data.meta_description: Quickly convert India Standard Time (IST) to Central European Time (CET) with this easy-to-use, modern time zone converter.
data.text:
Converting IST to CET

This time zone converter lets you visually and very quickly convert IST to CET and vice-versa. Simply mouse over the colored hour-tiles and glance at the hours selected by the column... and done!

IST stands for India Standard Time. CET is known as Central European Time. CET is 3.5 hours behind IST. So, when it is it will be
